flowRoot.flowPara: Get accurate true wind without calibration issues
The system automatically computes optimal parameters to better estimate true wind.
To evaluate the estimation quality, we compare the true wind direction before and after maneuvers.
The results shown here are computed from data collected onboard the 6mR Irene.
The system automatically collects performance statistics and computes target VMG as a function of wind speed.
The results in the figure below were computed and measured for the 8mR modern Yquem II.
